== Wescom Archive ==

This website allows full text searching of all stories, images and PDF pages published at The Bulletin from 1992-Present. Stories, images and PDF pages are ingested on a daily basis every morning and get added to the index on import. Indexing is handled by the Sunspot SOLR gem.

Installation
1) Configure Database.yml
2) Run 'rake db:migrate'
3) Run 'rails server'
4) Enjoy